        "title": "税收一体化何以影响企业税收遵从？",
        "url": "https://www.asc.net.cn/AccountingResearch/BrowseDetail.aspx?k=FF0DE4EE-13FF-4AA3-BE04-BE50BB8B83ED&ID=92F3F679-2BA1-4AAD-8190-C2D5AFE6B48B",
